Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}洋蔥大蒜土司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎呀 真的幫我泡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是你訂送的麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一直以來承蒙照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}壞掉的爐子修好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯哼哼~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯~ 沒什麼~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個... 洋蔥大蒜土司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊... 你的店裡也有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也是按照馬黛拉的製作方法製作的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬黛拉的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 別看馬黛拉這個樣子 其實很好管閒事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我剛來的時候 是最先照顧我的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}剛來的時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為是漂流者的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}科羅拉小姐也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼有以前的記憶嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有哦 完全都不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不在意嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個... 過去的... 事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}應該說 就算在意也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還是說已經發生了也沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是這樣啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且對我來說在這裡有必須要做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以抽個煙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下次我們的麵包店也提供咖啡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎... 這樣的話晚上來店裡一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}累死了啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真沒想到竟然會這麼忙呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然很感謝有這麼多人來捧場呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我搞錯了客人的飲料兩次了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那還好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}櫃台收銀我都弄得一團糟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要好好考慮一下了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼辦呢 要不要決定個負責人比較好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}總之咖啡一定要有個人幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}放棄麵包外送之類的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家原來都是漂流者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼有以前的記憶嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有哦 完全不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不在意嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個... 過去的... 事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}應該說 就算在意也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還是說已經發生了也沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然可能是這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 果然還是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}里克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}里克覺得怎麼樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的... 好好注意聽啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等店裡的善後能拜託你們嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為中午外送的麵包 大部分都交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:04.21,Title2,,0,0,0,,{\fs58\fad(450,400)\blur8\pos(640,625)}— 科羅拉·酒吧 —
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又說這種話啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}阿拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的過來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請坐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要點什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼... 就牛奶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}科羅拉！ 來一份洋蔥大蒜土司
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好意思 今天賣完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦 明明已經送到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唉... 一直以來都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請點些的其他的...吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡可是我的指定席啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊！ 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等一下 別隨便就亂說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}指定席是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我現在決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}笨蛋...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}里克 坐旁邊可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒看過的臉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}第一次來這邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬黛拉的徒弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是麵包師哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我叫里克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}噢 真有禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我叫迪蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是個船員
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}船員？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說的可真好聽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我沒說錯的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是這樣的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嘛... 說直接點就是海盜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}海盜！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不用這麼害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為我可是個好海盜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:10:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要戲弄這個煩惱的年輕人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼？ 在煩惱些什麼東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 我只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看著別人的臉龐就陷入沉思了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嘛 因為也是漂流者 所以也想過一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}關於過去自己的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}科羅拉小姐也這麼考慮過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}會是怎麼樣呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恩 是田園麵包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}追加一個田園麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}里克 追加一個田園麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}瞭解了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個麻煩拿去烤一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:10:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:10:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}羊角麵包只有盤子上這些而已嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天已經只剩這些而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好意思 明天的話會幫你先預留好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼就拜託你們了~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我在這裡的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是為了大家 做出美味的麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在這裡還有著必須要做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家 輝夜已經變得非常精神了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再過幾天應該就能自己走路了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了呢~ 輝夜！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能去外面的話 就能帶你參觀各種地方了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再來一個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家雖然失去記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是在這個陌生的溫達利亞島上 努力的活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}前兩天那個男孩 說過是個麵包師的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就是他做的麵包哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這不是挺好吃的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過在最近味道有些變化了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不就是偶爾狀態不好而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果只是這樣的話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}阿拉 歡迎光臨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晚安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你來了啊！ 煩惱少年
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以坐在你旁邊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊... 洋蔥大蒜土司？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}噢 不會給你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}平常不是都說賣完了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這間店的菜單上啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}剛開始的時候 就只有酒和大蒜土司而已哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}剛開始貼出這個菜單的時候 自己都覺得害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就拿下來 不就好了嘛~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也會有啊 怎樣都想堅持下去的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快點察覺到呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過就是個小女孩而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個... 科羅拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}漂流到這個島上之後...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的對自己的記憶沒做過考慮什麼的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是說過了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算在意也沒辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在雖然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以前呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗄~ 這種小事就別太在意了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在眼前有箱寶藏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成為領先的第一艘船 拿到手不就好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為你是個不講道理的人 才會說出這種話的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嘿~ 你說的沒錯啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我在店裡和大家一起做著麵包 外送給小鎮上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以決定把這種使命 當成自己的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然每天工作都很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過也有不少人 期待著我做出來的麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然也有過很辛苦的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有著支持我的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也有很多歡樂的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這不是一件很幸福的事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我覺得那是一件很幸福的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是... 我仔細想過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能夠這樣持續繼續下去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就這樣下去可以嗎... 之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對我來說 沒有漂流到這個島之前的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我想會不會有一天會被記憶絆住停滯不前呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:15:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}越是覺得現在過的很充實很幸福 就開始不安起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太年輕了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}覺得自己生存之道一點都沒錯的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在這世界上是不存在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然對和我一起生存的同伴來說不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}做海盜的 自己的過去常常被人討厭是家常便飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能夠知曉未來並且活在這個世上的人也是不存在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這種事情就隨他去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}反正洋流遲早都會到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:35.24,NOTE,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}洋流:寒暖流的分界線
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}洋流？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是持續漂流下去 就會有所改變
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到這個島上之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在海上看到了非常巨大的要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有可能會對小島上進行襲擊也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也有可能已經遠離這邊也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:16:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看不到這傢伙 未來的動向啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}會做什麼 誰都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以才會不安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是什麼都不做的話 不管什麼也不會開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嘛 反正還有考慮的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}失敗時候的時間也是後悔的時間也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}重新來過的時間也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有很充足的時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}未來還長的很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的未來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}輝... 輝夜！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦... 麵包師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}輝夜 你已經可以外出了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我在猶豫著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}猶豫什麼的...？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:16:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}里克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想要好好的看一次月亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}輝夜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}漂流到島上之前的事 還有什麼記得的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已經不記得了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也什麼都不記得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}里克... 想瞭解以前的自己嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不曉得...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一直以來好像都逃避著往這方面思考
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}輝夜什麼都沒想過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以後帶著心裡的創傷在這裡生活 不會害怕嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:17:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}醒過來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已經有里克陪著 還有大家也陪著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一直為我製作美味好吃的麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是因為想著什麼時候能夠醒來就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是我一定在心中的某個角落想著輝夜會持續昏迷不醒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能這麼和里克聊天 我很高興哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算什麼都不做 洋流也會到來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}持續漂流下去就會有所改變
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有些棘手的傢伙是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在這個島上可能會發生什麼也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乘上我的船也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你還是會再次救我逃離危險嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊... 不管幾次我都會...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看你的決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓女生搭上的船會沉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是個古板的女人啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.93,0:19:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我有著好好待在地面上的理由哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.52,0:19:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那你就好好待在這邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請問你要點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天也是一個人來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真了不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 謝謝~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天媽媽早上起來 幫我做了蜂蜜三明治哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎 真好啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了呢 里克
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天我沒訂送麵包啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個 請收下！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}洋蔥大蒜土司？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個... 和科羅拉談過之後 也變得輕鬆點了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個是還禮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊  謝謝你~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉啊 我也沒想到能幫上你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是 因為那個人 海盜的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}迪蘭？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再見到他的話 我想要再次的感謝他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他已經不在了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下次會是什麼時候來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}未來會發生的事情我沒辦法瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼... 如果方便的話我想請問一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}科羅拉在這裡必須要做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.83,0:21:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}媽媽~！ 媽媽~！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}歡迎回來 修
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我買回來了哦 麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}做出好吃的蜂蜜三明治給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好~的 得好好的努力一番了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.63,0:21:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了！~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.93,0:21:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蜂蜜三明治啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好... 痛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.89,0:21:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一下下就好了啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}媽媽 好痛的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來了~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.37,0:21:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我在等著你哦 漢克
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}城堡裡又有小偷事件了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.13,0:23:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}讓蘿娜變得很憂鬱呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.55,0:23:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}好啦~ 打起精神來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.18,0:23:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}今天一起進行愉快的野餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}為了下次也能做出幸福的麵包~
